يا ريت كل الموجودين في الجروب يلتزمو بقوانينه  في الاجابه على الأسئله و نقد الطروحات و الافكار من غير تجريح او اساءه لحد و يا ريت الأدمنز يقومو الأعضاء في حالات المخالفه

https://github.com/egyptian-geeks/FAQ/wiki/New-Members-Guidelines

please make sure you have noticed these two guides :

Be creative, come up with new idea, write your opinion "and support it with evidences and proper information", we appreciate opinions and posts that has some effort in it.

Be friendly, talk to people like in real life, use references for your replies, attack the problem, say your opinion, don't attack people.
